Pawel Szajda https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pawel_Szajda 0 Pawel B. Szajda (Polish: Paweł Szajda [ˈpavɛw ˈʂajda]; born January 13, 1982) is an American screen and stage actor. He is best known for his roles in Under the Tuscan Sun, Generation Kill and Tatarak.
